summary: Personal house inspired by Proudspire Manor. Requires Only Skyrim.esm & Update.esm
descriptionHtml:
My Personal Home inspired by Proudspire Manor.
Includes Cases, Mannequins, Weapon Racks & Plaques, and some General Storage.
Dragon Priest Mask Busts - Including Wooden Mask
Room with points to Almost Every City.
Room with Smithing/Alchemy/Enchanting Tools.
Custom Static Decorations

Coming Soon:
Bug fixes for Mannequin Underwear and Wooden Mask Reading as Krosis
Compatibility with World/City Changing Mods
Level 2 - Kitchen/Storage
False Backed Closet to "Safe"
More Mannequins/Cases/Chests/Racks & Plaques
Re-worked Level 1 - Skill Specific Areas with Merchants
--Versions for Base Game/Update and DLCs--

Known Bugs:
Alchemy Merchant won't Un-Aggro
Possible Incompatibility with World/City Changing Mods (Will Fix if Any Occur)
Mannequins Missing Underwear

This is my First Public Release
Criticize is Welcomed and Appreciated
Please let me know If Any Bugs are experienced and I'll attempt to fix them.
Suggestions Welcomed and will be Considered
author: RogueXxSniper
